OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784292510
OL,3,CLaos methanol poisoning families
OL,4,C'crushed' over expected charges
OL,6,FThe families of victims of the Laos
OL,7,Fmethanol poisonings are "crushed" over
OL,8,Fthe sentences expected to be given to
OL,9,Fthose believed to be responsible for
OL,10,Fmultiple deaths in 2024.
OL,12,FOn Friday, authorities in Laos are
OL,13,Fexpected to announce charges against
OL,14,Fthe suppliers, with penalties of up to
OL,15,Fa year in prison and a collective fine
OL,16,Fof around $1,117 (#830), according to
OL,17,Finformation received by the affected
OL,18,FAustralian families.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784292510
OL,3,CLaos methanol poisoning families
OL,4,C'crushed' over expected charges
OL,6,FThose responsible are not expected to
OL,7,Fbe charged with breaching hygiene
OL,8,Flaws, which would have added five
OL,9,Fyears to the sentence, according to
OL,10,FITV News' Australian partner 7News.
OL,12,FSix people, including 19-year-old
OL,13,FAustralian tourists Bianca Jones and
OL,14,FHolly Morton-Bowles, and 28-year-old
OL,15,FBrit Simone White, died after
OL,16,Fsuspected methanol poisoning at a
OL,17,Fhostel in Vang Vieng.
OL,19,FBianca and Holly's families have said
OL,20,Fthe penalties are "unacceptable".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
