OL,3,CLaos methanol poisoning families
OL,4,C'crushed' over expected charges
OL,6,FWhen they failed to check out as
OL,7,Fplanned, they were found ill in their
OL,8,Froom and were eventually evacuated to
OL,9,Fhospitals in neighbouring Thailand,
OL,10,Fwhere they later died.
OL,12,FMethanol is sometimes added to mixed
OL,13,Fdrinks at disreputable bars as a
OL,14,Fcheaper alternative to ethanol, but it
OL,15,Fcan cause severe poisoning or death.
OL,16,FIt is also a byproduct of poorly
OL,17,Fdistilled home-brew alcohol, and could
OL,18,Fhave found its way into bar drinks
OL,19,Finadvertently.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
